name: KartCompare
overview: KartCompare provides price comparison for products across a number of online stores in India. Currently the price comparison is done on mobile phones, books and cameras. Search for a product and we give you information like MRP, lowest price, number of sellers selling the product, shipping charges involved and direct product page links of the online stores. Along with this we provide product analysis like Price Chart which shows the historical price of the product. Review Section is for users who want to share their experiences or knowledge about the product. Apart from that we have product specifications listed for the users to make intelligent choice as per their needs.
